# BlockVote 🗳️

BlockVote is a decentralized and secure voting platform built on the **Aptos blockchain** using the **Move smart contract language**. It enables communities, organizations, and DAOs to conduct transparent, tamper-proof elections that are verifiable, auditable, and immutable.

## 🔍 Why BlockVote?

Traditional voting systems are prone to:

- Vote manipulation
- Centralized control
- Lack of transparency
- Voter exclusion

BlockVote solves these problems by leveraging the power of blockchain to guarantee:

✅ Transparent results  
✅ Immutable records  
✅ Anonymous and verifiable votes  
✅ Decentralized trust

## 🚀 Features

- 🧱 Built on Aptos with Move  
- 🌐 Fully decentralized voting  
- 🔒 End-to-end vote encryption  
- 👥 Supports DAOs, student unions, NGOs, and cooperatives  
- 🧠 Optional AI module for:
  - Detecting abnormal voting behavior  
  - Predicting turnout trends  
  - Real-time election analytics  

## 📦 Tech Stack

| Layer           | Technology                |
|----------------|---------------------------|
| Blockchain      | Aptos                    |
| Smart Contracts | Move                     |
| Frontend        | React (Planned)          |
| Wallet          | Martian, Petra           |
| AI Module       | Python (Planned)         |

